# UV Quick Reference for Intraday Trading Framework

## Initial Setup
uv sync --no-install-project    # Install all dependencies from uv.lock
source .venv/bin/activate       # Activate virtual environment

## Running Scripts
uv run python app.py            # Run without activating venv
uv run python test_e2e.py       # Run E2E tests

## Managing Dependencies
uv add pandas                   # Add new dependency
uv remove six                   # Remove dependency
uv sync                         # Sync environment with pyproject.toml

## Running Tests
uv run pytest                   # Run all tests
uv run pytest tests/test_coroutines.py  # Run specific test file

## Updating Dependencies
uv lock --upgrade               # Update all dependencies
uv lock --upgrade-package pandas  # Update specific package

## Development
uv run python -m pytest --cov   # Run tests with coverage
uv pip list                     # List installed packages
uv pip freeze                   # Show exact versions

## Useful Commands
uv venv                         # Create new virtual environment
uv python list                  # List available Python versions
uv python install 3.11          # Install specific Python version
